import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack} from '@chakra-ui/react';

const Headline = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container maxW="1364px" bg="tomato">
                <Stack direction="row" spacing="1250px">
                    <Box>
                        <Stack direction="column" spacing="40px">
                            <Box w="40px" h="40px" bg="yellow.200">
                                1
                            </Box>
                            <Box w="40px" h="40px" bg="gray.50">
                                2
                            </Box>
                            <Box w="40px" h="40px" bg="pink.100">
                                3
                            </Box>
                            <Box w="40px" h="40px" bg="pink.100">
                                4
                            </Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Box w="674px" h="629px" bg="yellow.200">
                            1
                        </Box>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Headline
